{"tid":971800,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂 - 泡菜豆腐鍋","createTime":"2019-01-07T02:29:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T14:00:50.000Z","uid":30742,"like":43,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fe585423bf2a9b49761c0072c1750500553c3820","tid":971800,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T02:29:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UnDbVxK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUnDbVxK.jpg&h=b2582dc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eczsx8Sc3jY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Feczsx8Sc3jY&d=QF%2F%2Fztc2otFsaDQ0jsNTvkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=ef72bcd5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eczsx8Sc3jY</a><br />\n<br />\n上星期post了醃泡菜，當然要做埋泡菜料理啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個湯冬天我基本上每星期至少做一次！<br />\n因為快、簡單、美味、暖笠笠！<br />\n用黎配飯、麵、粉絲都得<br />\n我都會配蒟蒻或芋絲<br />\n有時我們放泡菜放耐左，就咁食會太酸！<br />\n因為變左老泡菜，呢黎煮呢個就最好喇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n圖文食譜 <a href=\"https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2019/01/kimchi-stew-kimchi-jjigae.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.com%2F2019%2F01%2Fkimchi-stew-kimchi-jjigae.html&d=QF%2F%2Fztc2otFsaDQ0jsNTvkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=2f291df0\" target=\"_blank\">https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2019/01/kimchi-stew-kimchi-jjigae.html</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook專頁 : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=QF%2F%2Fztc2otFsaDQ0jsNTvkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=715c703e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F_oldlady_%2F&d=QF%2F%2Fztc2otFsaDQ0jsNTvkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=f29b8a49\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/</a><br />\nBlog: <a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F&d=QF%2F%2Fztc2otFsaDQ0jsNTvkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=04243f7f\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"a308bc2733e1ce440d6bbd6e56b670c830e7f197","tid":971800,"uid":65778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T02:35:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"636ec9740f11a8839dd864cd4466fd9d6fa1f207","tid":971800,"uid":128271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T02:35:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會唔會試下係公司整"},{"pid":"2af348290d10046e8cf08a9c5c86f1e680dd7495","tid":971800,"uid":63588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T02:36:39.000Z","msg":"又泡菜"},{"pid":"8d766f16ad979087c0aebbec8e4266dd49ef1acf","tid":971800,"uid":6562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"636ec9740f11a8839dd864cd4466fd9d6fa1f207","tid":971800,"uid":128271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T02:35:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會唔會試下係公司整"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T02:44:34.000Z","msg":"咁老娘用扇撥到手抽筋都唔掂WOR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22a5eeaef8fd5413a4ae0295356e04869633c5c8","tid":971800,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"636ec9740f11a8839dd864cd4466fd9d6fa1f207","tid":971800,"ui